posting_body: ['Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 11', 'OR Text', '11', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our team.', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 820 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Welcome to Arterra, a gorgeously landscaped community in Everett, WA offering newly renovated apartments and fabulous amenities.', 'Feel at home in a spacious, open-concept one or two bedroom apartment with nine-foot ceilings.', 'Gorgeous hardwood-style flooring and sleek stainless steel appliances in select homes will impress your guests.', 'Cozy up by the wood-burning fireplace or entertain your friends on your very own patio or balcony.', 'Laundry rooms, built-in desks and large closets ensure a convenient living experience.', 'Speak with the leasing team today to learn more.', 'Features:', 'Hardwood-Style Flooring*, Large Closets, Washer & Dryer in Unit, Renovated Homes**, Stainless Steel Appliances*, Garbage Disposals, Ceiling Fan, Wood Burning Fireplaces, Patio or Balcony, Cable & Internet Ready', '*In Select Units', 'Community Amenities:', 'Playground, Dog Park, Onsite Maintenance, Business Center, Easy Access to I5 & I405, Clubhouse, Onsite Management, Covered Parking, Near Public Transportation, Courtyard, Outdoor Fire Pit, BBQ & Picnic Area', 'Pet Policy', 'Arterra welcomes your pet!', 'Our apartments accommodate up to two pets per home, with no weight limit.', 'There is a $300 Pet Fee and Pet Deposit of $300.', 'Pet Rent is $30.', 'Breed restrictions apply.', 'Please call our leasing office for complete Pet Policy.', 'Interested in more information?', 'Visit link below:', '<URL>', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'J7sAFaE1B73']
